OL,3,CUK travellers face EU border system
OL,4,Cdelays for up to two years, official
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FA new EU border system causing long
OL,8,Fdelays for many UK travellers arriving
OL,9,Fin the bloc may not "stabilise" for
OL,10,Ftwo years, an official has warned.
OL,12,FUku Sarekanno, deputy executive
OL,13,Fdirector of EU border agency Frontex,
OL,14,Fsaid some member states are
OL,15,F"struggling" to adopt the Entry Exit
OL,16,FSystem.
OL,26,@qD@UOUqD@_O]tD@FxpwD@AOUwD@LO]
