OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781024765
OL,3,CUK travellers face EU border system
OL,4,Cdelays for up to two years, official
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FEES requires people from non-EU
OL,8,Fcountries, such as the UK, to have
OL,9,Ftheir fingerprints registered and
OL,10,Ftheir photo taken by passport
OL,11,Fofficials to enter the Schengen Area.
OL,13,FThe digital record is kept for three
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FThe International Air Transport
OL,17,FAssociation recently warned border
OL,18,Fqueues could reach six hours this
OL,19,Fsummer, with airports in Spain,
OL,20,FPortugal, France and Italy reported to
OL,21,Fbe among the worst affected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781024765
OL,3,CUK travellers face EU border system
OL,4,Cdelays for up to two years, official
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FMore than 100 easyJet passengers
OL,8,Fmissed a flight from Milan Linate to
OL,9,FManchester in April because of delays
OL,10,Fat passport desks caused by the
OL,11,Framping up of EES.
OL,13,FSpeaking to travel industry leaders at
OL,14,Fan ABTA-organised summit in
OL,15,FWestminster, Mr Sarekanno said: "We
OL,16,Fexpect that the situation will
OL,17,Fstabilise in one or two years.
OL,26,@wD@RxpwD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781024765
OL,3,CUK travellers face EU border system
OL,4,Cdelays for up to two years, official
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"The most challenging part is the
OL,8,Ffirst enrolment, that is, the moment
OL,9,Fwhere fingerprints and facial images
OL,10,Fwill be taken.
OL,12,F"If a person is visiting the EU again
OL,13,F(within three years), they don't have
OL,14,Fto go through the same process, so
OL,15,Fthey can have a more fast track of
OL,16,Fentry."
OL,18,FAbout 1,700 border crossing points
OL,19,Frequire the use of EES.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
