OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781024765
OL,3,CUK travellers face EU border system
OL,4,Cdelays for up to two years, official
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FMr Sarekanno went on: "Member states
OL,8,Fare still adjusting to the new
OL,9,Freality. There are ones which are
OL,10,Fmanaging it rather well, who have
OL,11,Fdedicated resources.
OL,13,F"There are the others who are still
OL,14,Fstruggling. This adjustment... is
OL,15,Ftaking some time and effort."
