OL,3,CUK travellers face EU border system
OL,4,Cdelays for up to two years, official
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FEES was introduced in October last
OL,8,Fyear, with its rollout ramped up on
OL,9,FApril 10.
OL,11,FEU rules currently allow the checks to
OL,12,Fbe temporarily halted to avoid queues
OL,13,Fat peak periods, but that is not
OL,14,Falways happening.
OL,16,FA recent survey commissioned by travel
OL,17,Fcompany Booking.com indicated that
OL,18,Fnearly three out of five (59%) UK
OL,19,Fholidaymakers travelling to Europe
OL,20,Fthis year expect delays linked to EES.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
